org.locationtech.geowave.core.geotime.store.dimension

Class TimeField

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.locationtech.geowave.core.geotime.store.dimension.TimeField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NumericDimensionDefinition, Persistable, NumericDimensionField<Time>

    public class TimeField
extends Object
implements NumericDimensionField<Time>
    This field definition can be used for temporal data (either as a time range or a single instant in time).
